>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯整傷沙拿都比你賤種話怨婦<br />\n你賤種蝗係唔係想做怨婦"},{"pid":"13be56ac17bf6d78f8aa2284137d3929fc39ba09","tid":703832,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:37:14.000Z","msg":"其實big gay好驚佢<br />\n可以上youtube睇下片<br />\n牙朗直係對決佢入波都有十幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdc241b1e65d0684de2c0330938e12486508cfc","tid":703832,"uid":157898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"so9.gif"},{"pid":"f5600827cf660a8b36610c88f320894a7c2c0aef","tid":703832,"uid":12034,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"2010年11月17日<br />\n<br />\n碧基發誓不會說C朗一句壞話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n本月底西班牙打吡即將上演，近期腳風頗順的C朗絕對是巴塞隆拿的心腹大患。不過賽前巴塞中堅碧基卻對他讃許有加。<br />\n「當初我加盟曼聯的時候，C朗就是球隊的頭號球星，你可以想像一下，當時像我這種毫無經驗的新人在更衣室有何地位？不過C朗卻幫助我很多，我發誓，我永遠不會說他的壞話。」碧基接受採訪時說。"},{"pid":"1846cf0b780c8b0e06820c191c9e068287cc633d","tid":703832,"uid":120965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"傻仔做德甲icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7542683d582bf803409f77f1c9638e9493a04c64","tid":703832,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"真係正一賤種西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}